snippet.title: cartels & cutthroats gameplay (PC Game, 1985)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Cartel$ & Cutthroat$, Dos PC game produced by SSI in 1985 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/cartels-cutthroats/12548/
Cartel$ & Cutthroat$ is, a challenging economic simulation that's equally educational and entertaining. In this game 1-8 players compete for profit in this simulation of cut-throat competition.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
